rmed%20the%20commencement%20of%20shooting%20through%20a%20video%20release%20on%20July%205.%20While%20specific%20plot%20details%20are%20tightly%20guarded%2C%20director%20Shiv%20Rawail%20has%20planned%20several%20action%20sequences%20for%20the%20initial%20filming%20phase.%20The%20storyline%20ventures%20beyond%20Mumbai%2C%20with%20the%20spy%20mission%20taking%20Alia%20and%20her%20co-star%20on%20a%20global%20adventure%2C%20including%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20where%20they%20will%20be%20mentored%20by%20Anil%20Kapoor's%20character.%20'Alpha'%20is%20YRF's%20first%20female-led%20Spy%20Universe%20film%2C%20directed%20by%20Shiv%20Rawail%2C%20known%20for%20his%20work%20on%20Netflix's%20acclaimed%20series%20'The%20Railway%20Men.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-begins-filming-for-yrfs-alpha-following-the-female-led-spy-universe-title-announcement%2Farticleshow%2F111627373.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Relief%20For%20Bengal%20In%20Case%20Against%20CBI's%20Sandeshkhali%20Probe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government's%20challenge%20to%20the%20Centre%20over%20the%20CBI%20investigating%20West%20Bengal%20cases%20without%20the%20state's%20consent%20is%20valid%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20came%20as%20a%20twist%20after%20the%20court%20recently%20allowed%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20multiple%20cases%20of%20sexual%20assault%20and%20land%20grabbing%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20-%20despite%20opposition%20from%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20government%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20CBI%20over%20filing%20cases%20despite%20the%20state%20withdrawing%20its%20general%20consent%20to%20the%20central%20agency%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20reserved%20the%20decision%20on%20May%208%20after%20hearing%20both%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20KV%20Vishwanathan%20today%20rejected%20the%20Centre's%20contention%20that%20the%20petition%20by%20Bengal%20was%20not%20maintainable%20and%20said%20the%20case%20would%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20federalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20considered%20the%20DSPE%20(Delhi%20Special%20Police%20Establishment)%20Act%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20rules.%20It%20cannot%20be%20said%20that%20West%20Bengal%20has%20not%20made%20out%20any%20case%20against%20Centre%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20section%206%20of%20the%20DSPE%20Act%2C%201946%2C%20the%20CBI%20must%20obtain%20consent%20from%20respective%20state%20governments%20to%20conduct%20investigations%20in%20their%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DSPE%20Act%20provides%20immunity%20from%20the%20Centre's%20powers%2C%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20find%20that%20in%20the%20present%20suit%2C%20the%20plaintiff%20is%20raising%20the%20legal%20issue%20of%20whether%20CBI%20can%20file%20a%20case%20under%20the%20DSPE%20Act%20after%20revocation%20of%20consent.%20Can%20CBI%20register%20and%20investigate%20cases%20in%20violation%20of%20Section%206%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20hearing%20is%20on%20August%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20currently%20probing%20multiple%20charges%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20land%20grabbing%2C%20and%20ration%20scam%20against%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%20-%20a%20former%20Trinamool%20leader%20and%20local%20strongman%20-%20and%20his%20aides%20in%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20government%20had%20opposed%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court's%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20case.%20Allowing%20the%20CBI%20to%20continue%20its%20probe%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20wondered%20why%20the%20Bengal%20government%20was%20interested%20in%20protecting%20an%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720595640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fbs64jvlo_sandeshkhali-violence_625x300_02_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-says-bengal-governments-petition-against-cbi-probe-into-sandeshkhali-case-without-its-consent-is-valid-6073100%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government's%20challenge%20to%20the%20Centre%20over%20the%20CBI%20investigating%20West%20Bengal%20cases%20without%20the%20state's%20consent%20is%20valid%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-says-bengal-governments-petition-against-cbi-probe-into-sandeshkhali-case-without-its-consent-is-valid-6073100%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-says-bengal-governments-petition-against-cbi-probe-into-sandeshkhali-case-without-its-consent-is-valid-6073100%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-says-bengal-governments-petition-against-cbi-probe-into-sandeshkhali-case-without-its-consent-is-valid-6073100%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mumbai%20BMW%20Hit-And-Run%3A%20Bulldozer%20Action%20At%20Pub%20Where%20Accused%20Spent%20Hours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESections%20of%20the%20bar%20in%20Mumbai's%20Juhu%20that%20served%20alcohol%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmihir-shah%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMihir%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2024%2C%20were%20demolished%20by%20city%20officials%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%2024%20hours%20after%20Excise%20Department%20officials%20sealed%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vice-Global%20Tapas%20Bar%20sold%20liquor%20to%20Shah%20-%20who%20is%2025%20