%20else%20can%20be%20said%20about%20crooked%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20you%20have%20to%20give%20him%20credit%20for%20one%20brilliant%20decision%2C%20probably%20the%20smartest%20decision%20he%20ever%20made.%20He%20picked%20Kamala%20Harris%20as%20his%20vice%20president.%20No%2C%20it%20was%20brilliant.%20Because%20it%20was%20an%20insurance%20policy.%20Maybe%20the%20best%20insurance%20policy%20I've%20ever%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20Donald%20Trump%2C%2078%2C%20told%20his%20supporters%20in%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Joe%20had%20picked%20someone%20even%20halfway%20competent%2C%20they%20would%20have%20bounced%20him%20from%20office%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20they%20can't%20because%20she's%20gotta%20be%20their%20second%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20he%20repeatedly%20mispronounced%20her%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20as%20vice%20president%2C%20Harris%20was%20given%20two%20very%20important%20tasks%20-%20border%20security%20and%20to%20deter%20Russia%20from%20attacking%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20she%20was%20put%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20U.S.%20border%20security.%20She%20never%20showed%20up.%20She's%20never%20gone.%20She%20never%20went%20there%20once.%20And%20the%20border%20is%20the%20worst%20border%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20best%20border%20in%20history%20because%20she%20has%20the%20worst%20border%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world.%20Then%2C%20she%20was%20sent%20to%20Europe%20to%20deter%20Russia%20from%20attacking%20Ukraine.%20How%20did%20that%20work%20out%3F%20Not%20too%20good.%20Both%20times%2C%20the%20result%20was%20a%20deadly%20failure.%20Since%20Kamala%20was%20made%20border%20czar%2C%20the%20Biden-Harris%20administration%20has%20lost%20track%20of%20an%20estimated%20150%2C000%20children%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20undoubtedly%20been%20raped%2C%20trafficked%2C%20killed%2C%20or%20horribly%20abused%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C