3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20complaint%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20BJP%20leader's%20allegations%20that%20Ms%20Parvathi%20benefited%20from%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20MUDA's%20land%20allotment.%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20said%20influential%20people%2C%20including%20the%20current%20Chief%20Minister's%20wife%2C%20received%20prime%20property%20in%20Mysuru%20as%20compensation%20for%20land%20MUDA%20acquired%20for%20layout%20development.%20They%20allege%20that%20the%20value%20of%20land%20provided%20as%20compensation%20is%20much%20more%20than%20the%20land%20acquired%20and%20that%20this%20caused%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20to%20the%20state%20exchequer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECharge%20Against%20Siddaramaiah%20Wife%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramiah%20has%20said%20the%20land%20his%20wife%20received%20compensation%20for%20was%20gifted%20by%20her%20brother%20Mallikarjuna%20in%201998.%20But%20activist%20Snehamayi%20Krishna%20has%20alleged%20that%20Mallikarjuna%20bought%20land%20in%202004%20and%20gifted%20it%20to%20Parvathi%20in%202010.%20This%20land%2C%20he%20has%20said%2C%20was%20already%20denotified%20but%20was%20falsely%20shown%20as%20agricultural%20land.%20Later%2C%20this%20was%20acquired%20by%20MUDA%20for%20development%20and%20Parvathi%20received%2038%2C283%20square%20feet%20of%20prime%20real%20estate%20in%20south%20Mysuru%20in%202021.%20The%20activist%20has%20alleged%20that%20Mallikarjun%20procured%20the%20land%20illegally%20and%20got%20it%20registered%20it%20using%20forged%20documents%20with%20the%20help%20of%20government%20and%20revenue%20officials.%20The%20land%20was%20shown%20to%20have%20been%20bought%20in%201998.%20Parvathi%20sought%20compensation%20for%20this%20land%20in%202014%2C%20when%20Siddaramaiah%20was%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Has%20Siddaramaiah%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20response%20to%20the%20BJP's%20offensive%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20said%20his%20wife%20was%20awarded%20compensation%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%20and%20that%20it%20was%20her%20right.%20%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP)%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20gave%20the%20site%2C%20now%20if%20they%20call%20it%20illegal%2C%20how%20should%20one%20respond%3F%20They%20took%20away%20our%20land%20and%20parks%20were%20made%20there%2C%20and%20those%20sites%20were%20allocated%20to%20others.%20Should%20we%20give%20up%20our%20land%20because%20I%20am%20the%20Chief%20Minister%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Opposition's%20Stand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20demanded%20a%20CBI%20investigation%20into%20the%20alleged%20irregularities.%20On%20the%20compensation%20provided%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20wife%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%20R%20Ashoka%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20land%20was%20acquired%20by%20MUDA%20and%20then%20denotified.%20I%20don't%20know%20on%20whose%20pressure%20it%20was%20done.%20After%20the%20denotification%2C%20MUDA%20formed%20a%20layout%2C%20park%20and%20playground%20on%20that%20land.%20This%20gives%20rise%20to%20many%20doubts%20because%20once%20it%20is%20denotified%2C%20MUDA%20has%20no%20right%20to%20touch%20that%20piece%20of%20land%2C%20which%20belongs%20to%20a%20reputed%20person.%20Yet%2C%20the%20layout%20was%20formed.%26quot%3B%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20Union%20minister%20and%20leader%20of%20BJP%20ally%20JDS%2C%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20MUDA%20row%20is%20an%20outcome%20of%20a%20power%20struggle%20between%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20his%20deputy%20D%20K%20Shivakumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720588560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fm9dajj3g_siddaramaiah_625x300_23_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsiddaramaiah-muda-big-charge-against-siddaramaiahs-wife-amid-mysuru-land-compensation-row-6072815%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20social%20activist%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife%20Parvathi%20and%20two%20others%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20alleged%20Mysore%20Urban%20Development%20Authority%20(MUDA)%20scam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsiddaramaiah-muda-big-charge-against-siddaramaiahs-wife-amid-mysuru-land-compensation-row-6072815%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsiddaramaiah-muda-big-charge-against-siddaramaiahs-wife-amid-mysuru-land-compensation-row-6072815%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsiddaramaiah-muda-big-charge-against-siddaramaiahs-wife-amid-mysuru-land-compensation-row-6072815%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gambhir%20Informs%20BCCI%2C%20Wants%20Ex%20RCB%20Star%20As%20Team%20India%20Bowling%20Coach%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ferocious%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20was%20named%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20by%20the%20BCCI%2C%20which%20hoped%20that%20he%20would%20bring%20%26quot%3Btenacity%20and%20leadership%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20position%20that%20was%20held%20with%20%26quot%3Bremarkable%20success%26quot%3B%20by%20Rahul%20Dravid%20until%20recently.%20Gambhir's%20arrival%20isn't%20the%20only%20change%20in%20India's%20coaching%20setup%2C%20with%20the%20former%20opening%20batter%20also%20looking%20to%20bring%20in%20his%20own%20coaching%20staff.%20While%20Abhishek%20Nayar%2C%20the%20assistant%20coach%20at%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%2C%20is%20one%20of%20Gambhir's%20preferences%2C%20he%20reportedly%20also%20wants%20former%20India%20and%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20pacer%20R%20Vinay%20Kumar%20as%20the%20bowling%20coach%20in%20the%20Indian%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRevSportzGlobal%2Fstatus%2F1810695695558713702%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERevSportz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gambhir%20has%20submitted%20the%20names%20of%20Abhishek%20Nayar%2C%20as%20assistant%20coach%20and%20R%20Vinay%20Kumar%2C%20as%20bowling%20coach%2C%20to%20the%20BCCI.%20WIth%20Gambhir's%20coaching%20tenure%20beginning%20with%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20series%2C%20the%20BCCI%20would%20need%20to%20act%20quickly%20upon%20the%20recommendations%20made%20by%20Gambhir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2042-year-old%20Gambhir%20was%20the%20front-runner%20to%20replace%20Dravid%20whose%20tenure%20ended%20with%20the%20country's%20title%20win%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20Barbados%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20an%20absolute%20honour%20to%20serve%20my%20tricolour%2C%20my%20people%2C%20my%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gambhir%20in%20a%20BCCI%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20congratulate%20Rahul%20Dravid%20and%20his%20team%20of%20support%20staff%20for%20their%20exemplary%20run%20with%20the%20team.%20I%20am%20honoured%20and%20excited%20to%20take%20on%20the%20role%20of%20Head%20Coach%20for%20Team%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20taken%20pride%20while%20donning%20the%20Indian%20jersey%20during%20my%20playing%20days%20and%20it%20is%20going%20to%20be%20no%20different%20when%20I%20take%20up%20this%20new%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20said%20he%20looks%20forward%20to%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20BCCI%2C%20Head%20of%20Cricket%20VVS%20Laxman%2C%20the%20support%20staff%2C%20and%2C%20%26quot%3Bmost%20importantly%2C%20the%20players%2C%20as%20we%20work%20towards%20achieving%20success%20in%20the%20upcoming%20tournaments.%26quot%3B%20Gambhir's%20first%20assignment%20as%20India%20coach%20will%20be%20the%20of%20tour%20Sri%20Lanka%20for%20three%20T20Is%20and%20as%20many%20ODIs%20starting%20July%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Board%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20former%20Head%20Coach%2C%20Mr%20Rahul%20Dravid%20for%20his%20brilliant%20run%20with%20the%20team.%20Team%20India%20now%20embarks%20on%20a%20journey%20under%20a%20new%20coach%20%E2%80%93%20Mr%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BCCI%20President%20Roger%20Binny%20in%20an%20elaborate%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20stated%20that%20the%20Cricket%20Advisory%20Committee%20comprising%20Ashok%20Malhotra%2C%20Jatin%20Paranjpe%20and%20Sulakshana%20Naik%20on%20Tuesday%20unanimously%20recommended%20Gambhir.%20The%20BCCI%20had%20invited%20applications%20for%20the%20position%20on%20May%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20experience%2C%20dedication%2C%20and%20vision%20for%20the%20game%20make%20him%20the%20ideal%20candidate%20to%20guide%20our%20team%20forward.%20We%20are%20confident%20that%20under%20his%20leadership%2C%20Team%20India%20will%20continue%20to%20excel%20and%20make%20the%20nation%20proud%2C%26quot%3B%20Binny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720588440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ff7h3h71o_gautam-gambhir-bcci_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-informs-bcci-wants-rcb-star-r-vinay-kumar-as-team-india-bowling-coach-report-6069948%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20has%20shared%20the%20names%20of%20his%20preferred%20assistant%20coach%20and%20bowling%20coach%20to%20the%20BCCI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-informs-bcci-wants-rcb-star-r-vinay-kumar-as-team-india-bowling-coach-report-6069948%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-informs-bcci-wants-rcb-star-r-vinay-kumar-as-team-india-bowling-coach-report-6069948%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-informs-b