oing%20to%20polls%20are%20Raiganj%2C%20Ranaghat%20Dakshin%2C%20Bagda%20and%20Maniktala%20in%20West%20Bengal%3B%20Dehra%2C%20Hamirpur%20and%20Nalagarh%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%3B%20Badrinath%20and%20Manglaur%20in%20Uttarakhand%3B%20Jalandhar%20West%20in%20Punjab%3B%20Rupauli%20in%20Bihar%3B%20Vikravandi%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Amarwara%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Four%20of%20these%20states%20are%20ruled%20by%20INDIA%20constituents%20while%20the%20rest%20have%20a%20BJP%20or%20NDA%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20electoral%20exercise%20will%20decide%20the%20fate%20of%20many%20veterans%20and%20some%20debutants%2C%20including%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu's%20wife%20Kamlesh%20Thakur%20from%20the%20Dehra%20constituency.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Sukhu%20government%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20has%20survived%20removal%20attempts%20and%20won%20bypolls%20in%20four%20out%20of%20six%20Assembly%20seats%20which%20were%20held%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Six%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20three%20Independents%20had%20cross-voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20nominee%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%20MLAs%20were%20disqualified%20and%20bypolls%20were%20held%20on%20those%20six%20seats%20earlier.%20The%20Independents%20resigned%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20and%20elections%20for%20their%20seats%20are%20being%20held%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BVote%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20not%20the%20MLA.%20Now%2C%20Dehra%20will%20also%20become%20the%20constituency%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister...%20I%20will%20not%20need%20to%20go%20to%20the%20Secretariat%20to%20get%20your%20work%20done%2C%20I%20will%20get%20it%20done%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Kamlesh%20Thakur%20told%20people%20while%20seeking%20votes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20stakes%20are%20high%20for%20both%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20-%20which%20beat%20all%20expectations%20and%20improved%20its%20tally%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20to%2029%20of%20the%20state's%2042%20seats%2C%20up%20from%2021%20in%202019%20-%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20whose%20figure%20went%20down%20from%2018%20to%2012.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Trinamool%20won%20the%20Maniktala%20seat%20in%20the%202021%20West%20Bengal%20Assembly%20elections%20while%20the%20BJP%20won%20Raiganj%2C%20Ranaghat%20Dakshin%20and%20Bagda.%20Later%2C%20the%20BJP%20MLAs%20switched%20to%20the%20Trinamool.%20The%20Maniktala%20bypoll%20has%20been%20necessitated%20by%20the%20death%20of%20sitting%20Trinamool%20MLA%20Sadhan%20Pandey%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUttarakhand's%20Manglaur%20constituency%20will%20witness%20a%20three-cornered%20fight%20in%20the%20bypoll%2C%20which%20is%20being%20held%20after%20the%20death%20of%20BSP%20MLA%20Sarwat%20Karim%20Ansari%20in%20October%20last%20year.%20The%20BJP%20has%20never%20won%20the%20Muslim-%20and%20Dalit-dominated%20Manglaur%20seat%20which%20has%20been%20held%20either%20by%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20BSP%20so%20far.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20all%20five%20seats.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Punjab%2C%20the%20bypoll%20in%20the%20Jalandhar%20West%20assembly%20segment%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20litmus%20test%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann.%20The%20AAP%20won%20only%20three%20of%20the%20state's%2013%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720576080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F5kqltfg8_elections-_625x300_10_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwest-bengal-bypolls-himachal-bypolls-key-polls-in-13-assembly-seats-today-first-since-lok-sabha-elections-6070260%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Of%20the%2013%20constituencies%2C%20four%20are%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20three%20in%20Himachal%2C%20where%20the%20Sukhwinder%20Singh%20Sukh