2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMax%20Levchin%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Affirm%2C%20always%20knew%20he%20would%20take%20his%20buy-now%2C%20pay-later%20fintech%20public.%20What%20he%20didn't%20know%20was%20the%20pandemic%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20economically%20uncertain%20times%20in%20history%2C%20would%20set%20Affirm's%20initial%20public%20offering%20into%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20definitely%20experienced%20a%20real%20moment%20where%20we're%20not%20yet%20profitable.%20We%20would%20need%20to%20raise%20money%20if%20we%20wanted%20to%20survive%20through%20what%20could%20be%20a%20drought%20in%20equity%20capital%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Levchin%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20first%20several%20months%20of%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20buffer%2C%20Affirm%20raised%20private%20capital%20in%20mid-2020%2C%20a%20process%20Levchin%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20huge%20pain%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20ton%20of%20uncertainty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20seem%20like%20curious%20timing%20to%20take%20your%20company%20public%20during%20a%20pandemic%2C%20but%20that's%20exactly%20what%20Max%20Levchin%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20buy-now%2C%20pay-later%20company%2C%20Affirm's%20business%20model%20was%20built%20on%20the%20promise%20of%20repayment%20as%20it%20enabled%20consumers%20to%20finance%20their%20online%20purchases.%20The%20pandemic%20became%20a%20boon%20for%20Affirm%20as%20Americans%20received%20stimulus%20checks%20and%20e-commerce%20boomed.%20Levchin%2C%20wanting%20to%20ride%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-now-pay-later-growth-timeline-fintechs-affirm-klarna-paypal-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20wave%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20needed%20more%20capital%20to%20grow%20the%20company.%20The%20sustained%20unpredictability%20in%20the%20private%20markets%20triggered%20talks%20of%20going%20public%2C%20but%20Levchin%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20doing%20so%20was%20a%20step%20in%20the%20journey%20and%20not%20an%20end%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20his%20doubts.%20%26quot%3BCan%20we%20head%20from%20the%20IPO%20into%2C%20'Go%20faster%20and%20harder%20and%20invest%20even%20more%20aggressively%20into%20interesting%20ideas%2C'%20or%20would%20we%20just%20suddenly%20stall%20and%20become%20a%20slow-moving%2C%20publicly%20traded%20sort%20of%20paralyzed%20giant%3F%26quot%3B%20Levchin%20said.%20Affirm%20shares%20were%20listed%20on%20January%2013%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20pipeline%20of%20IPOs%20starts%20to%20build%20up%20again%2C%20including%20the%20anticipated%20debut%20of%20Affirm's%20buy-now%2C%20pay-later%20rival%20Klarna%2C%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20Levchin%20about%20Affirm's%20IPO.%20He%20reflected%20on%20the%20decision-making%20process%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20offering%2C%20how%20he'd%20handled%20the%20peaks%20and%20valleys%20of%20Affirm's%20share%20price%2C%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20pieces%20of%20advice%20for%20founders%20contemplating%20going%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258bce776-ae22-4797-8303-2a4a3cb1b6c0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20late%20nights%20on%20Zoom%20to%20Nasdaq%20debut%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20cofounder%20of%20the%20payment%20juggernaut%20PayPal%2C%20Levchin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-now-pay-later-boom-creating-new-class-of-billionaires-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperienced%20firsthand%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20benefits%20of%20taking%20a%20fintech%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20was%20still%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%20more%20work%20than%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Levchin%20said.%20It%20wasn't%20uncommon%20for%20Levchin%20to%20be%20on%20Zoom%20with%20his%20CFO%20and%20chief%20legal%20officer%20at%2010%20p.m.%20with%20half-finished%20glasses%20of%20wine%2C%20jokingly%20asking%20why%20they%20did%20this%20to%20themselves%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20half%20of%202020%2C%20long%20days%20and%20late%20nights%20were%20spent%20auditing%20and%20cleaning%20Affirm's%20books%2C%20getting%20numbers%20and%20documents%20in%20order.%20Affirm's%20small%20IPO%20task%20force%20also%20needed%20to%20assemble%20critical%20documents%2C%20including%20the%20company's%20S-1%20and%20a%20founders'%20letter.%20Meanwhile%2C%20its%20chief%20legal%20and%20finance%20officers%20needed%20to%20vet%20a%20long%20list%20of%20bankers%20who%20jockeyed%20to%20represent%20Affirm%20during%20the%20frothy%2C%20low-interest-rate%20market%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffirm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.affirm.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Faffirm-files-registration-statement-with-sec-for-proposed-ipo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elanded%20on%20three%20banks%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20lead%20underwriters%20for%20the%20offering.%20Beyond%20having%20long-standing%20relationships%20with%20the%20companies%20pre-IPO%2C%20Levchin%20wanted%20partners%20who%20could%20%26quot%3Bspeak%20to%20our%20business%20at%20least%20as%20well%20as%20we%20could%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hard%20work%20seemed%20to%20pay%20off.%20When%20Affirm%20debuted%20on%20the%20Nasdaq%2C%20its%20share%20price%20surged%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Faffirm-stock-price-ipo-trading-debut-nasdaq-offering-levchin-afrm-2021-1-1029965771%3F_gl%3D1*wb8bmj*_ga*MzY0NDY1NTUzLjE2OTE3MTE3MDY.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTcxNTk2MzkxOS41MzguMC4xNzE1OTYzOTI5LjUwLjAuMA..%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20much%20as%20110%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20above%20its%20opening%20price%20of%20%2449.%20Affirm%20shares%20climbed%20to%20as%20high%20as%20%24164.23%20in%20late%202021%20but%20suffered%20the%20same%20stock%20rout%20that%20battered%20tech%20companies%20throughout%202022%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20major%20adjustment%20to%20being%20a%20public%20company%2C%20Levchin%20said%2C%20is%20not%20falling%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bquarterly%20lifestyle%26quot%3B%20where%20milestones%2C%20product%20road%20maps%2C%20and%20key%20metrics%20are%20divided%20into%20four-month%20sprints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20have%20this%20duality%20of%20mind%2C%20where%20being%20public%20is%20about%20the%20quarter%2C%20but%20it%20can't%20be%20just%20about%20the%20quarter%2C%26quot%3B%20Levchin%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20running%20a%20public%20company.%20If%20a%20quarter%20results%20in%20a%20number%20you're%20not%20proud%20of%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20can't%20just%20hammer%20yourself%20over%20the%20head%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Levchin%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20get%20worse%20if%20this%20quarter%20isn't%20pretty%2C%20but%20you%20know%20you're%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%2C%20and%20you%20can%20see%20in%20numbers%20that%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20OK.%20Don't%20stress%20it%2C%20and%20it'll%20work%20itself%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c6d5c7c-5af2-4328-b46b-77a208d837d3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWords%20of%20advice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20founders%20considering%20going%20public%2C%20Levchin%20offered%20some%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20uncommon%20to%20see%20startups%20hiring%20executives%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-08%2Fplaid-names-first-company-president-in-another-step-toward-ipo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuch%20as%20a%20president%20or%20CFO%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20anticipation%20of%20going%20public.%20But%20that%20could%20actually%20be%20a%20sign%20that%20you're%20not%20ready%2C%20Levchin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChemistry%20is%20critical%20to%20ensuring%20the%20IPO%20team%20is%20on%20the%20same%20page%20regarding%20what's%20right%20and%20wrong%20for%20the%20business.%20That's%20not%20something%20that%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Bformed%20and%20seasoned%20over%20the%20course%20of%20an%20IPO%20prep%2C%26quot%3B%20Levchin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevchin%20also%20warned%20against%20letting%20the%20process%20%26quot%3Bconsume%20the%20company.%26quot%3B%20He%20kept%20the%20team%20working%20on%20Affirm's%20plans%20very%20small%20because%20he%20wanted%20the%20day-to-day%20engine%20to%20continue%20humming%20along%20during%20the%20intense%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Affirm's%20CFO%20and%20chief%20legal%20officer%20largely%20spearheaded%20the%20IPO%20process%2C%20Levchin%20said%20he%20was%20left%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20company's%20short-%20and%20long-term%20plans%20for%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20deliberately%20plan%20for%20that%2C%20you%20may%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20just%20freezing%20in%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffirm-ceo-max-levchin-navigating-ipo-advice-future-founders-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720558991000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e112f20abc1efe8fc61ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffirm-ceo-max-levchin-navigating-ipo-advice-future-founders-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Affirm%20CEO%20Max%20Levchin%2C%20also%20a%20PayPal%20Mafia%20member%2C%20offers%20founders%20advice%20on%20getting%20IPO-ready%20based%20on%20lessons%20learned%20from%20his%20own%20public%20listing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Bianca%20Chan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffirm-ceo-max-levchin-navigating-ipo-advice-future-founders-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98When%20You%20Step%20Upon%20a%20Star%E2%80%99%20Chronicles%20Former%20Tabloid%20Write