0%9CI%20was%20wrong%20to%20judge%20you%20without%20seeing%20your%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20interviewed%20Romeeta%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20ponder%20how%20water%20has%20no%20ceiling%2C%20but%20even%20there%2C%20men%20have%20built%20a%20glass%20ceiling%2C%20which%20she%20successfully%20broke.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20gave%20you%20the%20strength%20and%20fortitude%20to%20face%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20colleagues%20were%20nice%20to%20me%20to%20my%20face%20but%20they%20all%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20not%20capable%20just%20because%20of%20my%20gender.%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20this%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fwp-admin%2Fadmin.php%3Fpage%3Dstats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproblem%20faced%20by%20women%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20land%20jobs%20too%3F%20All%20you%20can%20do%20is%20focus%20and%20work%20hard%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20keeping%20her%20chin%20up%20and%20focusing%20on%20excelling%20at%20her%20job%2C%20she%20silenced%20all%20her%20critics.%20Girls%20can%20do%20everything%2C%20she%20proved%2C%20rather%20emphatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Romeeta%20spent%20nine%20months%20on%20the%20ship%20during%20COVID-19%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-768x511.jpeg%20768w%2C%20http