%20with%20many%20organisations%20like%20Tribes%20India%2C%20simultaneously%20focussing%20on%20my%20research%20work.%20It%20all%20started%20with%20a%20college%20project%20but%20the%20more%20I%20got%20into%20it%2C%20I%20found%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20data%20on%20this%20waste%20and%20people%20only%20talk%20about%20plastic%20waste.%20So%20I%20wanted%20to%20draw%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20to%20butchery%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Radhesh%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20%E2%80%98Golden%20Feathers%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20upcycles%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98wool-like%E2%80%99%20fibre%20and%20handmade%20paper.%20Using%20this%20waste%20as%20raw%20material%2C%20the%20startup%20manufactures%20shawls%2C%20quilts%2C%20stoles%2C%20diaries%2C%20fish%20feed%20and%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20plastic%2C%20waste%20that%20needs%20urgent%20attention%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20family%20of%20doctors%20in%20Fatehpur%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Radhesh%20was%20expected%20to%20join%20the%20medical%20field.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20design%20and%20craft%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20pursue%20graduation%20in%20textile%20design%20from%20the%20Northern%20India%20Institute%20of%20Fashion%20Technology%20(NIIFT)%2C%20Mohali%2C%20and%20later%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Craft%2C%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20the%20students%20who%20come%20to%20study%20in%20these%20colleges%20are%20from%20affluent%20and%20superior%20backgrounds.%20They%20would%20come%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346052%2Findian-startups-turning-waste-into-eco-friendly-products-trash-to-treasure-watch-now%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elearn%20about%20design%20and%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20thoughts%20didn%E2%