-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355236%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMustafa%20P%20A%2C%20founder%20of%20Greenara%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20visited%20the%20land%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20there%20was%20not%20even%20a%20single%20tree%20on%20the%20property.%20Mining%20had%20taken%20away%20the%20life%20of%20the%20place%20but%20I%20could%20envision%20a%20greener%20future%20for%20the%20place.%20While%20I%20visited%20the%20place%20in%20summer%2C%20I%20could%20see%20the%20presence%20of%20water%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20the%20process%20of%20building%20an%20ecosystem%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20spend%20a%20year%20studying.%20He%20referred%20to%20various%20books%20and%20videos%20and%20spoke%20to%20people%20who%20had%20taken%20up%20such%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20by%20creating%20a%20huge%20pond%20and%20then%20divided%20it%20into%20streams%20throughout%20the%20property.%20This%20water%20became%20the%20main%20source%20of%20water%20for%20life%20to%20flourish%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20created%20six%20more%20ponds%20interconnecting%20them%20with%20the%20main%20one.%20%E2%80%9CI%20then%20planted%20saplings%20of%20trees%20as%20well%20as%20varieties%20of%20tropical%20plants%20I%20collected%20from%20different%20countries%20while%20travelling%20and%20trekking.%20I%20also%20purchased%20a%20few