itle%22%3A%22How%20To%20Grow%20Jackfruit%20Trees%20at%20Home%3F%20Gardener%20Shares%20Step-By-Step%20Guide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmidst%20monsoon%20delicacies%20like%20curry%20and%20fritters%2C%20jackfruit%20is%20a%20versatile%2C%20comforting%20and%20hearty%20meal%20packed%20with%20flavours.%20But%20did%20you%20know%20the%20flesh%20and%20seeds%20of%20jackfruit%20are%20also%20well%20known%20for%20their%20antibacterial%2C%20antifungal%2C%20and%20antidiabetic%20properties%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJackfruit%20helps%20strengthen%20bones%2C%20prevents%20bone-related%20disorders%20like%20osteoporosis%2C%20anaemia%2C%20aids%20blood%20circulation%2C%20and%20supports%20thyroid%20gland%20metabolism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20grow%20this%20superfood%20at%20home%2C%20we%20have%20got%20you%20covered!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELucknow-based%20urban%20gardener%20Abhijeet%20Prajapati%2C%20who%20has%20been%20growing%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20on%20his%20terrace%20for%20the%20last%20several%20years%2C%20shares%20tips%20on%20how%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F244522%2Fmaharashtra-konkan-farmer-jackfruit-trees-varieties-sapling-nursery-buy-ratnagiri%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivate%20jackfruit%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20grow%20jackfruit%20in%20an%20open%20space%20of%20your%20house.%20But%20if%20you%20lack%20open%20space%2C%20you%20can%20still%20harvest%20jackfruit%20by%20growing%20its%20tree%20in%20a%20big%20container%20or%20a%20grow%20bag%20on%20the%20terrace%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhijeet%20says%20that%20jackfruit%20can%20be%20planted%20from%20seeds%2C%20cuttings%20or%20saplings%20bought%20from%20the%20nursery.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20when%20planted%20from%20seeds%2C%20it%20may%20take%20about%20seven%20years%20for%20it%20to%20bear%20fruit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20you%