0from%20the%20market%20and%20sow%20its%20seeds.%20In%20place%20of%20seeds%2C%20you%20can%20also%20directly%20plant%20its%20sapling%20in%20the%20container.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20seeds%20germinate%20in%20about%20a%20week%20but%20the%20cuttings%20may%20take%20more%20than%20a%20month%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJackfruit%20trees%20need%20ample%20sunlight.%20Ensure%20the%20plant%20is%20positioned%20where%20it%20can%20receive%20at%20least%20six%20to%20seven%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20daily.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20watering%20the%20plant%2C%20ensure%20that%20water%20does%20not%20stagnate%20in%20the%20container%2C%20while%20also%20retaining%20enough%20moisture%20in%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20takes%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20before%20your%20plant%20starts%20growing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdd%20organic%20manure%20like%20liquid%20manure%20and%20vermicompost%20to%20the%20plant.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMake%20sure%20that%20pests%20do%20not%20attack%20the%20stem%20and%20leaves%20of%20the%20plant.%20Use%20organic%20pesticides%20like%20neem%20oil%20to%20check%20insect%20attack.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20what%20are%20you%20waiting%20for%3F%20This%20season%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337560%2Fkathalfy-founder-aman-chhabra-brings-jackfruit-ready-to-eat-product-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20your%20own%20jackfruit%20tree%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20gardening!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6339770%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520flesh%2520and%2520seeds%2520of%2Crelated%2520disorders%2520such%2520as%2520osteoporos