e%20has%20been%20scaling%20since%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShruthi%20delves%20straight%20into%20the%20details%20of%20this%20fascinating%20journey%20over%20a%20Zoom%20call%2C%20from%20the%20living%20room%20of%20her%20home%20in%20Jakarta%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20where%20she%20is%20currently%20based.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20compelling%20as%20her%20story%20is%2C%20I%20am%20intrigued%20by%20what%E2%80%99s%20behind%20her.%20Shruthi%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20of%20the%20eco-friendly%20decor%20she%20has%20created%20through%20her%20brand%20%E2%80%98Ombak%E2%80%99%20proves%20to%20be%20an%20apt%20description%20as%20my%20gaze%20follows%20the%20pieces%20set%20in%20the%20backdrop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20beauty%20equals%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20surpasses%20%E2%80%94%20mainstream%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295373%2Feconiture-turns-plastic-waste-into-sustainable-furniture-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecor%20alternatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20often%20manufactured%20using%20plastic%2C%20finished%20wood%20and%20treated%20fabrics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20%E2%80%98Ombak%E2%80%99%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98a%20large%20wave%E2%80%99%20in%20Bahasa%20(the%20language%20spoken%20in%20Indonesia)%2C%20Shruthi%20wants%20to%20urge%20consumers%20to%20invite%20sustainability%20into%20their%20homes%20for%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%2C%20eventually%20making%20it%20a%20permanent%20fixture%20in%20their%20daily%20lifestyles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20from%20a%20management%20professional%20engaged%20in%20business%20development%20for%20five%20years%20to%20an%20entrepreneur%20has%20had%20its%20share%20of%20twists%20and%20turns.%20And%20there%20was%20one%20pivotal%20moment%20that%20marked%20the%20shift.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20oversee%20design%20and%20marketing%20for%20brands%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20space%20as%20part%20of%20m